<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870828-0150 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News:LAC Minerals Ltd.</HL><DD> 08/28/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> LACDIVIDENDS (DIV) </IN><TEXT>   LAC MINERALS LTD. holders approved a 3-for-1 stock split, payable Sept. 18 to stock of record Sept. 10. LAC, a Toronto-based gold mining concern, has 30.5 million shares outstanding. LAC said its shares will begin trading on a post-split basis Sept. 3 on the Toronto Stock Exchange and Sept. 21 on the New York Stock Exchange. </TEXT></DOC>